New DP and edit work for @r3hab x @nowunited 

I traveled to Saudi Arabia to a really special place called AlUla to shoot this video. Thank you so much @malekalhamami & @nuhail_kusaibati for this opportunity, I’m now in love with a region that previously I knew very little about. Such a blast working with the NU team and choreographer @nickyandersen. Swipe for production & rehearsal BTS.

Massive thanks to the amazing team that helped piece this together with me.
One of my favorite shoots to date. Thank you to @fish_vizion and @masonprendergast for agreeing to a collaborative approach with the cinematography, thanks to the entire crew for bringing your A game. Cheers to @coltonjackson_12 and @company_3 for putting a bow on the piece. Thank you to @willbrandt & @rachellegoulding for all that you brought to the project. Special thanks to @take7productions for the support.

‘Collapsing Sky’ / Alfa Romeo

Check out slide 7 for the 30 second version. Full cut in bio. Special thanks @altovisuals & to the entire amazing crew that got involved.

‘Hedina’ // From the archives with @damien.blue @codylaplantfilms @bmir 🎥 shot inside an underground windowless apartment I once called home.

My project for Alfa Romeo was accepted into the @motorfilmawards festival in London, playing on the big screen tonight to a big audience full of other phenomenal directors and car lovers. Really wish I could have flown out for this one. Huge thanks to everyone at @tiltamax & @motorfilmawards for including my work and hosting such a cool niche film event. 🏎️
